<title>USA: Kroger Co Q1 oper net rises.</title>
<headline>Kroger Co Q1 oper net rises.</headline>
<dateline>CINCINNATI 1997-04-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>1997			1996</p>
<p> Oper shr diluted	  $0.69		    $0.59</p>
<p> Oper net		   92,260		   76,490</p>
<p> Revs		    6,139,413		5,784,254</p>
<p> Avg shrs diluted	133,588		  130,611</p>
<p>(All Data Above 000s Except Per Share Numbers)</p>
<p>NOTES: Share results exclude effect of two-for-one stock split announced in March.</p>
<p>Oper nets exclude debt retirement charges $5.2 million or $0.04 per share versus $1.1 million or $0.01 per share.</p>
